- cs.CE (Computational Engineering) is also likely as the software system is related to optimization of pumping energy costs for oil pipelines. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.OH (Other Computer Science) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper mentions the use of optimization models and experts from different fields. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the software system is related to controlling energy costs for oil pipelines.
